<DIV>Remember everyone that this is just the <U><STRONG>START</STRONG></U> of the class re envision process.&nbsp; There is supposed to be more to come in the future.&nbsp; They said this is the easy to do now/ things we have been working on so far stuff.&nbsp; I would also like to remind peeps that the&nbsp;top 10 list is things we want, not&nbsp;what Sony will do.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>As far as most of the changes go I think the ones related to us are all pretty good and for the better.&nbsp; I might actually complete my OoW spell set with the 66 dot. =P&nbsp; I am really looking forward to when the number crunching is done and they address the DPS issues though.</DIV>
