			>
			<DIV>Overall this is a step in the right direction. <img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-wink.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0> We will see what the final out come is when they go over the DPS issues of classes. I do agree with what is being said here, Beastlords are a utility class, Jack of all Trades...Master of None type class. At the level 65-70 We are group buffers, Slowers and DPS. We&nbsp;need group buffs. Im so sick of recasting single player buffs on the whole group. Group can sit there for 10 minutes while I finish casting OR they pull before Im done just to get things going leaving me out of the fight. I in no way want the power of a Shaman but a Group IoS, Ect ect that have already be gone over above is needed. Haste spell is a joke, Every other fight Im recasting it. Pet heals do need to be shorter casting BUT I also would like to see the pet ability to hold up vs a mob better. This in itself can open a can of worms, but Why do Mage pets out tank mine?? Are we not the Pure Pet Class?? My Pet should be just as tough (if not tougher) then any pet in the game.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Zesh</DIV>	
