<DIV>Like I said Can-o-Worms. Mage Vs Beastlords Pet issue has always been an on going battle. I don't want to go there here. All Im saying is our pets should be able to take a better punch then they do now. In DoN/OoW/GoD my pet is dead faster then I can hit the Heal button let alone the 9 sec cast timer.( if more then one mob is pulled and I need it to off tank for a few moments.) I feel the Warder should share the physical atributes of its Master. ie: AC....AA Defence Ability...Ect.</DIV>
