<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
Sikkem wrote:<BR>
<DIV>This may seem strange but I personally was hoping for a statement of what SoE see as the role/s of the beastlord.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>So do we take it from this list that no one has any idea what our role is or do SoE see our role as third choice slower?</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>What is the Vision?</DIV><BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>/agree Sikkem</P>
<DIV></DIV>
<P>It would be nice if they actualy "Defined" our class so we know what we need to be asking for. But I think SoE has no Idea what to think of us. We seem to fit the "Jack of all Trades" Role. We have split into 2 types of Beastlords: Pet Clerics &amp; Melee Beasts. The Majority of us&nbsp;are into the Melee Beast's Shoes. As a result alot of us are sceaming for DPS type issues, while the Pet Clerics are screaming for Pet Heal type issues. If they came out and said "Ok Beastlords are a Utility DPS class" Or "Beastlords are a Utility Pet Cleric"&nbsp;we as a whole would know what to be asking for in our own play style.</P>
<P>This isnt a major thing to Define Beastlords. It just would be nice to know what the Devs are thinking when they try to address our issues. What is our place in this world of Norrath? We all can make our assumptions on what we are, but only the Dev team can really say one way or another.</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>Zesh</P>	
